29:13.919 --> 29:15.687 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
LESLIE DIETZ: No.

29:15.721 --> 29:18.056 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARK TRUDELL: I haven't heard
