people work

29:41.647 --> 29:42.648 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
to do it.

29:42.681 --> 29:43.949 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
But they don't see it.

29:43.982 --> 29:46.084 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
They don't -- they don't come
down here and
look at this.

29:46.118 --> 29:50.889 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: Donald Trump
has made campaign
stops in rural parts of the
country, including

29:50.922 --> 29:54.493 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
