thinking about it.

30:33.498 --> 30:38.537 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Maybe there's economic
hardships, but it's
on the other side of town or the
other side

30:38.570 --> 30:42.040 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
