31:05.797 --> 31:10.035 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Darla Dietz, she's going to try
to make it
to a polling place on Election
Day, if she

31:10.068 --> 31:13.772 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
