her husband.

31:13.805 --> 31:18.810 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And for Leslie Dietz, she says
politicians
offer her nothing, and she turns
to faith

31:18.844 --> 31:20.278 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
instead.

31:20.312 --> 31:24.082 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
