31:25.984 --> 31:30.088 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LESLIE DIETZ: I kind of feel
strongly about
teaching them in Sunday school,
because I

31:30.122 --> 31:35.494 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
can make sure that they know the
difference
between right and wrong, what's
moral, what's

31:35.527 --> 31:38.029 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
ethical, you know?

31:38.063 --> 31:43.135 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I really don't want to get
