have a role
here or not?

40:05.069 --> 40:06.304 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
GEN.

40:06.337 --> 40:08.306 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVID PETRAEUS: It is essential
that the U.S.
has a role.

40:08.339 --> 40:13.578 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
