are now more
expensive on the shelf.

44:03.107 --> 44:07.879 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And how can we compete with
those producers
that wouldn't have this tax?

44:07.912 --> 44:16.220 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: We met up with
