45:06.837 --> 45:07.805 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JEFF JOHNSON: No.

45:07.838 --> 45:09.607 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
No, it doesn't.

45:09.640 --> 45:13.311 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
