George W.
Bush's Council of Economic
Advisers, finds

48:16.093 --> 48:18.662 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
a revenue-neutral carbon tax so
appealing.

48:18.696 --> 48:20.731 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GREGORY MANKIW, Former Chairman,
Council of
Economic Advisers: The first
principle of

48:20.765 --> 48:22.867 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
