to incentives.

48:22.900 --> 48:28.405 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And what a carbon tax tries to
do is tries
to harness that principle to get
people to

48:28.439 --> 48:30.241 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
