48:30.274 --> 48:36.046 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: But there is a case
to be made,
isn't there, that we ought to
invest in clean

48:36.080 --> 48:40.951 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
